{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_11_01",
  "title": "小美山愛 1話 最高のMVを作ってみせます",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日もリズノワは遅くまで練習か。BIG4になって）\n（しばらく経つけど、練習熱心なのは相変わらずだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（LizNoir’s practicing late again today. It’s been a while）\n（since they became BIG4‚ but their dedication to practice hasn’t changed.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.323598668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "さっきのところ、今までで一番合いましたね！\nみなさん、忘れないうちにもう一回やってみませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That last part—was the most in sync we’ve ever been!\nEveryone‚ shall we run it one more time before we forget?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6552384694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（ん？　いつもの練習風景と少し違うような……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Hm? This practice feels a little different from usual…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5599096935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの莉央さん、すっごくかっこ良かったです！\nでも、左手の振りをもっとこうした方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san just now was so cool!\nBut maybe if you move your left hand more like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.3567124049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "そう、そうです！　最高の最高にかっこいいです！\nそんな、私が頼もしいだなんて……えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that’s it! It's absolutely and unbelievably cool!\nMe? Reliable? Oh my… hehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5900457382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、こころ！　今のところ、なんかしっくり\nこなかったよね。一緒に葵さんに見てもらわない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Kokoro! That part just now felt a bit off‚ didn’t it?\nShall we ask Aoi-san to take a look with us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9567124049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（へぇ……愛が率先して練習を引っ張ってるのか）\n（BIG4になって、心境の変化があったみたいだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Heh… Ai’s taking the lead in practice.）\n（After becoming BIG4‚ it seems her mindset has changed.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、お疲れ様です！\n練習に夢中で気付きませんでした、すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san‚ good work!\nI was so absorbed in practice I didn’t notice you. Sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ついさっき来たばかりだから気にしないでくれ\nそれよりMV撮影に向けてレッスン、頑張ってるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just got here a moment ago‚ so don’t worry about it.\nMore importantly‚ you’re working hard for the MV shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "頑張り屋なのは相変わらずだが\nBIG4になってからの愛は凄く頼もしいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re still a real hard worker as always‚\nbut since becoming BIG4‚ you've been incredibly dependable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1251970269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、そうですか？\n頼もしいって言葉、今は一番嬉しいかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ really?\nBeing called dependable might be the nicest thing I’ve heard recently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3298414866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "『Grab the BIG4』が始まった頃は\n莉央さんと葵さんを支えるのが役目だと思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When “Grab the BIG4” first started‚\nI thought my role was to support Rio-san and Aoi-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7965081532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "でもセミファイナルのステージの前に\nこころと話して、少し考えが変わったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But before the semifinals stage‚\nafter talking with Kokoro‚ my mindset changed a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7631748199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "支えるんじゃなく、自分こそがLizNoirだ\nお二人と本当の意味で並んで立つんだ！　……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Instead of just supporting them—I am LizNoir.\nI’ll stand truly side-by-side with the two of them! …That’s what I decided.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "だから今は、莉央さんや葵さんの背中を\n追いかけるだけの、ただの後輩じゃなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So now‚ instead of just being a junior\nwho’s always chasing after Rio-san and Aoi-san‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9965081532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "隣に並ぶ仲間として、頼りにしてもらえるように\n出来ることは積極的にやろうと思ってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to actively do whatever I can\nto become a comrade who stands beside them and can be relied on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……大きく意識が変わったんだな\n俺の目から見ても、愛は凄く成長していると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… your outlook’s really shifted.\nEven from my perspective‚ Ai has really grown.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5224657078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "褒めていただけて嬉しいです！\n試行錯誤した甲斐がありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so happy you complimented me!\nAll that trial-and-error was worth it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3342239864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "試行錯誤？　どんなことをしたんだ？\n良かったら俺にも教えてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Trial-and-error? What kind of things did you try?\nIf you don’t mind‚ tell me too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2999964397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、強靭な精神は強靭な肉体に宿ると思って\nまずは筋トレを二倍に増やしました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ I believe a strong spirit resides in a strong body—\nso I doubled my strength training first!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.2979102452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "に、二倍！？\nそれは……オーバーワークになってないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "D-doubled!?\nIsn’t that… bordering on overwork?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.1999964397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん大丈夫です！\nちゃんと、自分の調子を見ながらメニューを決めました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I’m fine!\nI set the routine while properly checking my condition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.1818095843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "それから、格闘技の体験教室に行ってみたんです\n体験だけでも気が引き締まりましたよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I even tried a martial-arts trial class.\nEven just the trial really sharpened me up~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.9818095843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "か、格闘技！？　鍛えることに本当に妥協がないな\n怪我が少し心配だが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-martial arts!? You really don’t compromise when it comes to training.\nI’m a bit worried about injuries though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.5999954224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……というか、格闘技の楽しさに目覚めて\nそっちの道に進む、なんてことはない……よな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re not actually going to fall in love with martial arts\nand decide to go down that road full-time… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.4228634593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そんなことありえません！　それに今は\n時間が取れないから、本格的に習うのは見送りました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ that could never happen! Besides‚ right now‚\nI don’t have time. So I postponed learning it seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.9952335992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "でも、凄く勉強になりました。声を出すことの大切さや\n体の動きの一つ一つに意図を持たせることとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it was very instructive. The importance of projecting your voice‚\nand giving intention to each movement of the body—things like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.14979895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな。そんな試行錯誤が\n愛の成長に繋がっているんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. So those trial-and-error\nare what led to Ai’s growth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.4333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_11_01-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "今は、LizNoirのためにもっと何かしたくて\n自分に出来ることを探してる最中なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ I want to do more for LizNoir‚\nand I’m looking for what I can do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.0019572892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
